com.installshield.util.process
Class ExecuteProcessSupport

java.lang.Object
  com.installshield.util.process.ExecuteProcessSupport
public class ExecuteProcessSupport
extends Object

This support class encapsulates the information about a process launched natively on a target system. This class is used by the SystemUtilService.executeProcess() method and stores process execution status, return code, and user credentials
